response.overview: King Diamond returned to Wacken on August 2nd 2025 with his signature falsetto, coffins, spotlights, and a stage production that exists somewhere between a horror film and a heavy metal opera.  Setlist: "Arrival", "A Mansion in Darkness", "Halloween", "Voodoo", ""Them"", "Spider Lilly", "Two Little Girls", "Sleepless Nights", "Out from the Asylum", "Welcome Home", "The Invisible Guests", "The Candle", "Masquerade of Madness", "Eye of the Witch", "Burn", "Abigail"
response.title: King Diamond Live at Wacken 2025
